  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 1st level, your ability with Genjutsu easily eclipses others within the same field of expertise. <br />When you would cast a Genjutsu that requires concentration. <br />You reduce the cost to maintain all Genjutsu by an amount equal to their rank (D-Rank: 1, C-Rank: 2, B-Rank: 3, A-Rank: 4, S-Rank: 5.). <br />Your genjutsu concentration costs can be reduced to 0, regardless of what other features dictate.</p>",
